{"tid":135194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中移動又故障 手機冇訊號用戶fb再洗版","createTime":"2017-02-26T07:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T02:44:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27ccaf2761477e5dddd9bd9b37fc8b823aa7b595","tid":135194,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170226/large/1488092255_cac5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170226%2Flarge%2F1488092255_cac5.jpg&h=90ecec61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 「訊號零格，都唔係一次！」中移動下午發生故障，用戶的電話沒有訊號及網絡。這是中移動兩個半月內第二次故障，網民嬲爆在fb專頁「洗版」表達不滿！<br />\n<br />\n下午近2時，多名中移動用戶，發現手機完全沒有訊號，與今年1月故障時，出現的狀況一樣，有人「傾傾吓電話無訊號！」致電客戶查詢熱線又接不通，感到非常激氣，紛紛在中移動的fb專頁表達不滿。<br />\n<br />\n至下午3時04分，中移動在其fb專頁解釋，是由於電力配套故障，導致客戶嘅數據及話音服務可能受到影響，並盡力搶修，對受影響客戶深表抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n今年1月4日中午時份，中移動亦因出現電力配套故障問題，引致部分客戶的話音及流動數據服務受到影響，搶修逾3小時始陸續恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170226/56356106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170226%2F56356106&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn28n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=26b0e0ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170226%2F56356106&h=29e966b0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170226/56356106</a>"},{"pid":"1a0136a3ddbfedb5c26f51b465e9280704b3b9c0","tid":135194,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T07:27:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母支狗移 係咪俾人屌少一日都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"154de507ca810f1cbe0964da871a05e2f9ce3f66","tid":135194,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply